/console-doesnt-display-constellation). Nobody sees constellation so they cannot download SSH keys.\r\n\r\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>It seems that two people cannot connect to the field computer via the router at the same time (from two different stations): each time one logs in, the second is logged out (via SSH)\nThe problem might be caused by the fact that everyone is using the same keys.\nEveryone is using the same keys because of the problem <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/cloudsim/issue/60/console-doesnt-display-constellation\" rel=\"nofollow\">#60</a>. Nobody sees constellation so they cannot download SSH keys.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "open", "version": {"name": "1.2", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/cloudsim-legacy/versions/50247.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-03-14T07:08:27.734137+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-07-23T00:20:37.352849+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 61}